*.VC.db

# JetBrains Rider
.idea/

# ========== OS generated files ==========
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# ========== Unity Cloud Build ==========
/builds

# ========== Addressables ==========
/[Aa]ssets/[Aa]ddressable[Aa]ssets[Dd]ata/*/*.bin*

